			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "BIOS负责实际启动你的操作系统。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-tibhyin",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-tibhyin",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "在BIOS设置中，"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "你通常可以配置启动顺序，如CD-ROM、硬盘1、硬盘2等，以及它们的任何组合。BIOS会根据你的启动顺序偏好找到第一个可启动项。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-8jaazvw",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 3,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-8jaazvw",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "传统BIOS的局限性"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-wdw08c8",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-wdw08c8",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "由于引导加载程序大小的限制，大多数操作系统不得不使用复杂的链式启动过程。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-c7epjc2",
			"Type": "NodeHeading",
			"HeadingLevel": 4,
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-c7epjc2",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "传统BIOS启动过程"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-pypcgir",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-pypcgir",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "对于硬盘来说，存在一个引导扇区。引导扇区，或者更具体地说，是主引导记录（MBR），它包含引导加载程序，并且其大小限制实际上是440字节，"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "因此仅凭这个大小的引导加载程序绝对无法加载现代操作系统。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-9br5mtg",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-9br5mtg",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "通常，​"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "MBR中的引导加载程序会将控制权传递给活动分区的引导加载程序"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "​（VBR，卷引导记录），但它"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "strong",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "也有相同的大小限制。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-2mm7u20",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-2mm7u20",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "加载操作系统至少意味着引导加载程序必须从磁盘读取内核（Linux/Windows等）并将其控制权交给它。内核更加智能，能够理解各种文件系统，如NTFS/FAT等。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-vpfqp2w",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-vpfqp2w",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "但是，为了让引导加载程序从磁盘读取内核，**它必须知道如何遍历文件系统以访问内核。**因此，引导加载程序会从文件系统的根目录读取并链式加载一个“第二阶段”（这是一个更简单的任务）——一个可以更大、因此可以包含更复杂代码的文件。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-qbckvzu",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-qbckvzu",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "在Windows中，这个第二阶段过去被称为NTLDR（“NT加载程序”），它位于你的 "
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeTextMark",
					"TextMarkType": "code",
					"TextMarkTextContent": "C:"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "​驱动器的根目录下。"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20240924161727-vv4ep21",
			"Type": "NodeParagraph",
			"Properties": {
				"id": "20240924161727-vv4ep21",
				"updated": "20240924161727"
			},
			"Children": [
				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "​"
				},
				{
					"Type": "NodeImage",
					"Data": "span",
					"Children": [
						{
							"Type": "NodeBang"
						},
						{
